Aggregation.SQLExpression:
"N$10008" as (SELECT t0."CID", t0."APPLE_SUM", t0."BANANA_SUM", t0."MANGO_SUM", t0."MELON_SUM", t0."ORANGE_SUM", t0."PAPAYA_SUM", t0."PINEAPPLE_SUM" FROM (SELECT "CID", SUM("APPLE") "APPLE_SUM" ,SUM("BANANA") "BANANA_SUM" ,SUM("MANGO") "MANGO_SUM" ,SUM("MELON") "MELON_SUM" ,SUM("ORANGE") "ORANGE_SUM" ,SUM("PAPAYA") "PAPAYA_SUM" ,SUM("PINEAPPLE") "PINEAPPLE_SUM" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE}
GROUP BY "CID") t0 )
